data.description: What an amazing home nestled on a wooded lot with so many great features. This home has an open floor plan with the family room, eat-in kitchen all open up for family enjoyment and entertaining. Enjoy the separate living room and dining room. The upstairs has 4 bedrooms 2 full baths all very spacious and accommodating for space and living. The home is located close to great shopping, schools and entertainment. Only 20 minutes from the Atlanta Airport. Don't wait! Please note selling As-Is.
